    matvaretabellen2020
    Nutrient database mainly from the 2020 edition of the Norwegian food composition datatable Matvaretabellen.
    matvaretabellen2020_query
    Query words used to search through and map recipe ingredients to matvaretabellen2020. One or two words to map ingredients to matvaretabellen2020 dataframe.
    pcs
    A character vector of ingredients that when lacking a unit descriptor in recipe is counted as a piece, ie "3 kiwis" will be interpreted as "3 pieces of kiwi".
